和民居酒屋今正式关闭深圳万象城店，成疫情下首家撤退日企。
And residential Wine House today officially closed Shenzhen Vientiane Shengdian, the first Japanese evacuation under the epidemic situation.
卢奕贝。
LU Yick Pui.
