来源：品牌官网记者：卢奕贝编辑：牙韩翔“ 此前，经营不善已让和民陆续关掉了在中国内地的大部分门店。
www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cn www.youtheme.cnYouTheme (wwwyoutheme.cn) www.youtheme.cnYouTheme (wwwyoutheme.cn)
”开了16年的日式居酒屋“饗和民”深圳万象城店在今天正式结束营业了。
The Vientiane Shopping Mall in Shenzhen, a Japanese-style wine house for 16 years, officially closed today.
根据微信公众号“深圳吃货小分队”的报道，该店铺门口已经贴上了闭店通知，表示因合约到期以及公司品牌战略调整，公司决定于2020年3月1日起正式关闭饗和民万象城店。
According to the Weixin Public "Shenzhen Food Task Force," the store has posted a closing notice saying it will officially close the city shop on March 1, 2020 due to the expiration of the contract and changes in the company's brand strategy.
和民深圳万象城店门口的闭店通知。
Close shop notice at the entrance of Vientiane City, Shenzhen, China.
来源：深圳吃货小分队和民（Watami）是一个日本大众居酒屋连锁品牌，主要出售日式料理、日式小食、酒类等食品。
Source: Shenzhen EatSmart and Watami, a chain of Japanese popular liquor houses, mainly sell Japanese food, Japanese snacks and alcoholic drinks.
2001年，品牌母公司和民集团在香港开出了第一家海外分店，2005年正式进入内地，陆续在深圳、上海成立公司，经营和民居酒屋、饗和民、內亭等品牌。
In 2001, the parent company of the brand and Min Group opened its first overseas branch in Hong Kong. In 2005, it formally entered the Mainland and established companies in Shenzhen and Shanghai.
此前，和民集团曾于2月5日发表声明表示，由于新冠肺炎疫情导致其在中国的店铺营业时间缩短，来店顾客数量以及销售业绩都呈大幅下降趋势，加之对疫情平息时间无法预估，将在今春前退出中国市场。
The company said in a statement on Feb. 5 that it would pull out of the Chinese market by spring because of a reduction in shop hours, a sharp drop in the number of customers and sales results due to the outbreak, and an unpredictable time frame.
此次将关闭该集团在中国内地仅剩的11个门店中的7家直营店，其余4家因合约问题无法立即停业。
Seven of the group's remaining 11 stores in mainland China will be shut down this time, while the remaining four will not be able to close immediately because of contractual problems.
同时，香港及台湾地区的分店将继续营业。
Meanwhile, branch offices in Hong Kong and Taiwan will continue to operate.
这也是疫情发生以来，首家从中国内地撤退的日本企业。
It was also the first Japanese company to withdraw from mainland China since the outbreak.
和民集团在中国内地的发展曾有过辉煌。
The development of Wemin Group in mainland China has been brilliant.
2014年的巅峰时期，在中国大陆地区的店铺数量达到42家，此后几年也一直保持着迅猛的发展势头。
At its peak in 2014, the number of stores in mainland China reached 42, and has been growing rapidly for years to come.
到2016年，和民集团曾宣布要重组中国业务，计划与海航集团旗下的餐饮企业新设立合资公司，将店铺经营由直营方式转换为合资加盟方式，将加速在未进驻地区开店，计划尽快将中国大陆的店铺数量增加3倍，达到100家。
By 2016, HMG had announced plans to restructure its China operations, set up a new joint venture with HNA's catering operations, converting their operations from direct to joint ventures, and would accelerate the opening of stores in unoccupied areas, with plans to triple the number of stores in mainland China to 100 as soon as possible.
2017年，海航集团旗下爱其原味餐饮（HMV Cultural F＆B）宣布收购和民中国业务（上海、深圳、广州及苏州）60%股权。
In 2017, HMV Cultural F & B, a unit of HMG, announced a 60 per cent stake in HMF China (Shanghai, Shenzhen, Guangzhou and Suzhou).
但好景不长，和民此后在中国内地的经营并不顺利。
But it was not long before HMin's subsequent operation in mainland China did not go smoothly.
虽然财报中并没有公布中国内地业务的具体数据，但根据2019年3月公布的2018年度财报，这一年，因“无利可图”，和民集团已经关闭了在中国内地的12间门店，仅剩13家。
While the results do not disclose specific figures for mainland China, the company closed only 13 stores in mainland China that year because it was "unprofitable," according to the 2018 annual report released in March 2019.
此前，和民因经营不善，已关闭了在中国内地的12家门店。
Previously, Hutchison had closed 12 stores in mainland China because of poor management.
来源：财报截图100家门店的开店计划也随着2019年和民集团宣布取消合并，并完成回购和民（中国地区）60%股权，戛然而止。
Source: Financial report screenshots of 100 stores plan to close with the announcement in 2019 of a merger and the completion of a 60 per cent buy-back and Min (China) stake.
然而此后和民在中国内地的经营情况并没有好转，关店的脚步也没有停歇。
Since then, however, China and the people in mainland China's business situation has not improved, the pace of closing shop has not stopped.
截至2020年初，和民集团在中国上海、深圳、广州等地仅拥有有11家店铺，其中的7家直营店分别是“和民”上海SOHO复兴广场、深圳东门店、深圳九方广场、广州高德置地广场、苏州泉屋百货，“三文鱼传说和民”上海大宁国际、“迎和民”深圳华润万象城。
By early 2020, Wemin Group had only 11 shops in Shanghai, Shenzhen and Guangzhou, of which seven were directly owned by Wa Min Shanghai, SOHO Renaissance Plaza, Shenzhen Dongmendian, Shenzhen Jiufang Square, Guangzhou Goldfield Plaza, Suzhou Quan Uk Department Store.
经营不善、陆续关店的和民集团本已是处在危机的边缘，而新冠肺炎疫情的爆发，让全中国的餐饮行业都陷入被动。
The poorly run, closing and people's groups are already on the brink of crisis, and the outbreak of the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic has left the catering industry in a passive state across China.
根据中烹协调研数据，相比去年春节，疫情期间，78%的餐饮企业营收损失达100%以上；9%的企业营收损失达到九成以上。
Compared with the Spring Festival last year, 78 percent of catering enterprises lost more than 100 percent of their income, and 9 percent suffered more than 90 percent of the total.
而恒大研究院的数据显示，仅在春节七天内，疫情已对餐饮行业零售额造成5000亿元左右的损失。
In just seven days of the Lunar New Year, the epidemic has cost the restaurant industry about 500 billion yuan, according to the Hang Seng Institute of Research.
和民集团也最终下定决心，彻底退出中国内地市场。
HMG also made a final decision to withdraw completely from the Chinese mainland market.
